During the launch of the NFT Lion Cubs Brave souls of the NFT Jungle minted 84 NFT Lion Cubs these cubs have moved to a new contract.

The original 84 have turned into certificates of appreciation for being the first #NFTLionCubs of the NFT Jungle.
